<p>Team Greece secured an early lead with their entrée featuring perfectly cooked prawns, while Team Vietnam's Rice Paper Rolls unravelled with undercooked Morton Bay Bug. </p>

<p>Team Vietnam evened the score with a perfect main dish of Pork Belly with Bitter Melon Soup, scoring 30/30. </p>

<p>Meanwhile, Team Greece lost some points in the main by not resting their lamb after a stressful cook. </p>

